# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

The below versions of Bingo Caller are being supported

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 1.x   | :x:                 |
| 2.x   | :x:                 |
| 3.x   | :x:                 |
| 4.x   | :white_check_mark: |
| 5.x   | :white_check_mark:                |
| 6.x   | :white_check_mark: |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

Go to Issues and select 'Vulnerability issue'
